        {
            "_id": "vj9Tir2Y4G9lHyJb",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Cloven Charge",
            "sort": 500000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The House Thrune elite infantry charges forward with an infernal yell on cloven hooves. The troop Strides up to twice its Speed. At the end of the troop's movement, each enemy within a @Template[type:emanation|distance:10] takes @Damage[(2d6+7)[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage with a @Check[reflex|dc:34|basic] save.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": []
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "vflRjjd5NHRkgg3m",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Crossbow Array",
            "sort": 600000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The House Thrune elite infantry unit draws, loads, and fires a barrage from its crossbows. The salvo is a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] within 100 feet that deals @Damage[5d8[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage (@Check[reflex|dc:34|basic] save). When the elite infantry is reduced to 2 segments, this area decreases to a @Template[type:burst|distance:5].</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
